---
import { ArrowUpRight, Mail } from '@lucide/astro';
import { formatDate, profile } from '../data/site';
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-identity">
      <p><strong>손찬양</strong><span>Backend Engineer</span></p>
      <h2>운영 문제를 재현 가능한 수정으로 남깁니다.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-contact">
      <p>경력, 설계 판단과 테스트 근거를 한 사이트에서 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button button--secondary" href="mailto:cyson21@kakao.com" aria-label="손찬양에게 이메일 보내기"><Mail size={17} aria-hidden="true" /> 이메일</a>
        <a
          class="button button--text"
          href="https://github.com/cyson21"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          aria-label="손찬양 GitHub 프로필 새 창에서 열기"
        >GitHub <ArrowUpRight size={16} aria-hidden="true" /></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container footer-base">
    <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Son Chanyang</span>
    <span>최근 수정 <time datetime={profile.updatedAt}>{formatDate(profile.updatedAt)}</time></span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    padding-block: 58px 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--graphite);
    color: white;
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(320px, 0.55fr);
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .footer-identity > p {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .footer-identity > p strong {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-identity > p span {
    padding-left: 14px;
    border-left: 1px solid #5b6662;
    color: #b8c1bd;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
  }

  .footer-grid h2 {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .footer-contact {
    display: grid;
    gap: 22px;
    color: #d7dcda;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .site-footer .button--secondary {
    border-color: #69716e;
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
  }

  .site-footer .button--secondary:hover {
    border-color: #8ab9ff;
    background: #26364e;
  }

  .site-footer .button--text {
    color: white;
  }

  .footer-base {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid #424846;
    color: #aeb5b2;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .footer-base {
      flex-direction: column;
      margin-top: 44px;
    }
  }
</style>
